captions.text:
Loen TV viewers.
Hello! We're Teen Top!

We're back with the 4th mini album
Teen Top Class!

Let me tell you about
Teen Top Class.
We strived to show our unique color well.
I'll let you know Cringe Dance.

The foot work...
Go back and forth.

For this one,
you should focus on footwork.

Cross your legs diagonally.
Repeat it twice.
If you repeat it twice, it's perfect.
Stretch your arms side to side.
Move your left hand to the right side.
Do it the other way around.
Jump and raise the right leg.
And jump and raise the left leg.

We taught you the point dance
one by one, slowly.
It must be easy to follow, right?
It's good for your health as well.

We hope you dance this
at home all the time.

This has been
Teen Top's Let's Dance!
